Name: Form Has No Label
Description: Ensures every form element has a label
Help: Form elements must have labels

Name: Select Has No Label
Description: Ensures select element has an accessible name
Help: Select element must have an accessible name

Name: Area Has No Label
Description: Ensures <area> elements of image maps have alternate text
Help: Active <area> elements must have alternate text

Name: Low Color Contrast
Description: Ensures the contrast between foreground and background colors meets WCAG 2 AA minimum contrast ratio thresholds
Help: Elements must meet minimum color contrast ratio thresholds

Name: Link Has No Label
Description: Ensures links have discernible text
Help: Links must have discernible text

Name: Accesskey Not Unique
Description: Ensures every accesskey attribute value is unique
Help: accesskey attribute value should be unique

Name: Frame Has No Label
Description: Ensures <iframe> and <frame> elements have an accessible name
Help: Frames must have an accessible name

Name: Aria Input Has No Label
Description: Ensures every ARIA input field has an accessible name
Help: ARIA input fields must have an accessible name

Name: Marquee Is Used
Description: Ensures <marquee> elements are not used
Help: <marquee> elements are deprecated and must not be used

Name: Dialog Has No Label
Description: Ensures every ARIA dialog and alertdialog node has an accessible name
Help: ARIA dialog and alertdialog nodes should have an accessible name

Name: Object Has No Label
Description: Ensures <object> elements have alternate text
Help: <object> elements must have alternate text

Name: Progress Bar Has No Label
Description: Ensures every ARIA progressbar node has an accessible name
Help: ARIA progressbar nodes must have an accessible name

Name: Blink Is Used
Description: Ensures <blink> elements are not used
Help: <blink> elements are deprecated and must not be used

Name: Landmark Has Bad Structure (multiple main)
Description: Ensures the document has a main landmark
Help: Document should have one main landmark

Name: Landmark Has Bad Structure (duplicated)
Description: Landmarks should have a unique role or role/label/title (i.e. accessible name) combination
Help: Ensures landmarks are unique

Name: Landmark Has Bas Structure (not contained with landmark)
Description: Ensures all page content is contained by landmarks
Help: All page content should be contained by landmarks

Name: Landmark Has Bas Structure (nested)
Description: Ensures the complementary landmark or aside is at top level
Help: Aside should not be contained in another landmark

Name: Skip Link Not Focusable
Description: Ensure all skip links have a focusable target
Help: The skip-link target should exist and be focusable

Name: Table Header No Label
Description: Ensures table headers have discernible text
Help: Table header text should not be empty

Name: ARIA With Error (unsupported attributes)
Description: Ensures an element's role supports its ARIA attributes
Help: Elements must only use supported ARIA attributes

Name: ARIA With Error (disallowed roles)
Description: Ensures role attribute has an appropriate value for the element
Help: ARIA role should be appropriate for the element

Name: ARIA With Error (wrong attribute usage)
Description: Ensures ARIA attributes are used as described in the specification of the element's role
Help: ARIA attributes must be used as specified for the element's role

Name: ARIA With Error (deprecated roles)
Description: Ensures elements do not use deprecated roles
Help: Deprecated ARIA roles must not be used

Name: Body Uses Aria Hidden
Description: Ensures aria-hidden=true" is not present on the document body."
Help: aria-hidden=true" must not be present on the document body"

Name: ARIA With Error (disallowed attributes)
Description: Ensures ARIA attributes are not prohibited for an element's role
Help: Elements must only use permitted ARIA attributes

Name: ARIA With Error (required attributes missing)
Description: Ensures elements with ARIA roles have all required ARIA attributes
Help: Required ARIA attributes must be provided

Name: ARIA With Error (role with invalid value)
Description: Ensures all elements with a role attribute use a valid value
Help: ARIA roles used must conform to valid values

Name: ARIA With Error (aria with invalid value)
Description: Ensures all ARIA attributes have valid values
Help: ARIA attributes must conform to valid values

Name: ARIA With Error (invalid attributes)
Description: Ensures attributes that begin with aria- are valid ARIA attributes
Help: ARIA attributes must conform to valid names

Name: Small Line Spacing
Description: Ensure that text spacing set through style attributes can be adjusted with custom stylesheets
Help: Inline text spacing must be adjustable with custom stylesheets

Name: Bypass Not Supported
Description: Ensures each page has at least one mechanism for a user to bypass navigation and jump straight to the content
Help: Page must have means to bypass repeated blocks

Name: Document Has No Label
Description: Ensures each HTML document contains a non-empty <title> element
Help: Documents must have <title> element to aid in navigation

Name: Aria Has Duplicated ID
Description: Ensures every id attribute value used in ARIA and in labels is unique
Help: IDs used in ARIA and labels must be unique

Name: Heading Is Empty
Description: Ensures headings have discernible text
Help: Headings should not be empty

Name: Heading Has Bad Structure (order)
Description: Ensures the order of headings is semantically correct
Help: Heading levels should only increase by one

Name: Lang Is Missing
Description: Ensures every HTML document has a lang attribute
Help: <html> element must have a lang attribute

Name: Lang With Error (invalid)
Description: Ensures the lang attribute of the <html> element has a valid value
Help: <html> element must have a valid value for the lang attribute

Name: Image Has No Label
Description: Ensures elements have alternate text or a role of none or presentation
Help: Images must have alternate text

Name: Image Has Duplicated Label
Description: Ensure image alternative is not repeated as text
Help: Alternative text of images should not be repeated as text

Name: Landmark Has Bad Structure (banner not at root)
Description: Ensures the banner landmark is at top level
Help: Banner landmark should not be contained in another landmark

Name: Landmark Has Bad Structure (contentinfo not at root)
Description: Ensures the contentinfo landmark is at top level
Help: Contentinfo landmark should not be contained in another landmark

Name: Landmark Has Bad Structure (duplicated banner)
Description: Ensures the document has at most one banner landmark
Help: Document should not have more than one banner landmark

Name: Landmark Has Bad Structure (duplicated contentinfo)
Description: Ensures the document has at most one contentinfo landmark
Help: Document should not have more than one contentinfo landmark

Name: Link Not Clearly Visible
Description: Ensure links are distinguished from surrounding text in a way that does not rely on color
Help: Links must be distinguishable without relying on color

Name: List Has Bad Structure (li structure)
Description: Ensures that lists are structured correctly
Help: <ul> and <ol> must only directly contain <li>, <script> or <template> elements

Name: List Has Bad Structure (li missing)
Description: Ensures <li> elements are used semantically
Help: <li> elements must be contained in a <ul> or <ol>

Name: Zoom Limited
Description: Ensures <meta name=viewport"> can scale a significant amount"
Help: Users should be able to zoom and scale the text up to 500%

Name: Zoom Disabled
Description: Ensures <meta name=viewport"> does not disable text scaling and zooming"
Help: Zooming and scaling must not be disabled

Name: Nested Interaction Elements
Description: Ensures interactive controls are not nested as they are not always announced by screen readers or can cause focus problems for assistive technologies
Help: Interactive controls must not be nested

Name: Heading 1 Missing
Description: Ensure that the page, or at least one of its frames contains a level-one heading
Help: Page should contain a level-one heading

Name: Presentation Should Be Ignored
Description: Elements marked as presentational should not have global ARIA or tabindex to ensure all screen readers ignore them
Help: Ensure elements marked as presentational are consistently ignored

Name: Scrollable Region Not Focusable
Description: Ensure elements that have scrollable content are accessible by keyboard
Help: Scrollable region must have keyboard access

Name: Table Label Duplicated
Description: Ensure the <caption> element does not contain the same text as the summary attribute
Help: tables should not have the same summary and caption

Name: Table Has Bad Structure (td)
Description: Ensure that each cell in a table that uses the headers attribute refers only to other cells in that table
Help: Table cells that use the headers attribute must only refer to cells in the same table

Name: Table Has No Data Cell
Description: Ensure that <th> elements and elements with role=columnheader/rowheader have data cells they describe
Help: Table headers in a data table must refer to data cells

Name: Lang Wtih Error (invalid language)
Description: Ensures lang attributes have valid values
Help: lang attribute must have a valid value

Name: Aria Hidden Has Focusable Element
Description: Ensures aria-hidden elements are not focusable nor contain focusable elements
Help: ARIA hidden element must not be focusable or contain focusable elements

Name: Form Has Multiple Labels
Description: Ensures form field does not have multiple label elements
Help: Form field must not have multiple label elements

Name: Form Button Has No Label
Description: Ensures input buttons have discernible text
Help: Input buttons must have discernible text

Name: Input Has No Label
Description: Ensures that every form element has a visible label and is not solely labeled using hidden labels, or the title or aria-describedby attributes
Help: Form elements should have a visible label

Name: Autocomplete Not Valid
Description: Ensure the autocomplete attribute is correct and suitable for the form field
Help: autocomplete attribute must be used correctly

Name: Button Has No Label
Description: Ensures buttons have discernible text
Help: Buttons must have discernible text

Name: Tabindex Not Valid
Description: Ensures tabindex attribute values are not greater than 0
Help: Elements should not have tabindex greater than zero

Name: Description List Has Bad Structure (dl structure)
Description: Ensures <dl> elements are structured correctly
Help: <dl> elements must only directly contain properly-ordered <dt> and <dd> groups, <script>, <template> or <div> elements

Name: Description List Has Bad Structure (dl missing)
Description: Ensures <dt> and <dd> elements are contained by a <dl>
Help: <dt> and <dd> elements must be contained by a <dl>

Name: Landmark Has Bad Structure (main not at root)
Description: Ensures the main landmark is at top level
Help: Main landmark should not be contained in another landmark

Name: Landmark Has Bad Structure (duplicates)
Description: Ensures the document has at most one main landmark
Help: Document should not have more than one main landmark

Name: ARIA Role Bad Structre (no required children exist)
Description: Ensures elements with an ARIA role that require child roles contain them
Help: Certain ARIA roles must contain particular children

Name: ARIA Role Bad Structre (no required parent exist)
Description: Ensures elements with an ARIA role that require parent roles are contained by them
Help: Certain ARIA roles must be contained by particular parents

Name: Lang with Error (conflicting language)
Description: Ensure that HTML elements with both valid lang and xml:lang attributes agree on the base language of the page
Help: HTML elements with lang and xml:lang must have the same base language

Name: ARIA Role Has No Label
Description: Ensures every ARIA button, link and menuitem has an accessible name
Help: ARIA commands must have an accessible name

Name: Aria Image Has No Label
Description: Ensures [role=img"] elements have alternate text"
Help: [role=img"] elements must have an alternative text"

Name: Frame With Error (duplicated title)
Description: Ensures <iframe> and <frame> elements contain a unique title attribute
Help: Frames must have a unique title attribute

Name: Image Button Has No Label
Description: Ensures <input type=image"> elements have alternate text"
Help: Image buttons must have alternate text

Name: SVG Image Has No Label
Description: Ensures <svg> elements with an img, graphics-document or graphics-symbol role have an accessible text
Help: <svg> elements with an img role must have an alternative text

Name: Table Has Bad Structure (scope)
Description: Ensures the scope attribute is used correctly on tables
Help: scope attribute should be used correctly

Name: Tooltip Has No Label
Description: Ensures every ARIA tooltip node has an accessible name
Help: ARIA tooltip nodes must have an accessible name

Name: Treeitem Has No Label
Description: Ensures every ARIA treeitem node has an accessible name
Help: ARIA treeitem nodes should have an accessible name

Name: Should Not Refresh Through Meta
Description: Ensures <meta http-equiv=refresh"> is not used for delayed refresh"
Help: Delayed refresh under 20 hours must not be used

Name: Toggle Has No Label
Description: Ensures every ARIA toggle field has an accessible name
Help: ARIA toggle fields must have an accessible name

Name: Frame Not Focusable
Description: Ensures <frame> and <iframe> elements with focusable content do not have tabindex=-1
Help: Frames with focusable content must not have tabindex=-1

Name: Media Autoplay
Description: Ensures <video> or <audio> elements do not autoplay audio for more than 3 seconds without a control mechanism to stop or mute the audio
Help: <video> or <audio> elements must not play automatically
